i-MSCP RoundcubePlugins plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 1.0.0
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Compatible with Roundcube 1.x (version 1.x renamed main.inc.php to config.inc.php)
	Fixed: PO server will be checked. Some plugins only work with dovecot
	Fixed: send_request removed from imscp_pw_changer (sql.php)
	
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
